==English==
===Etymology===
Coined by [[w:Emile Berliner|Emile Berliner]] from Greek ''[[γραμμα]]'' a letter +''[[φωνη]]'' a sound.
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''gramophone'''
#{{obsolete}} a [[record player]], an instrument for recording or reproducing sounds especially characterized by recording on a disk rather than a cylinder.

===Derived terms===
*[[gramophone record]]
